channel.title: Y'all Pick - canned. Pkr/Town 2.0 wins (depending on interpretation)
channel.description:
## Welcome to Yall pick, where the apostrophe is very inconsistent @NightX and @Htm will be my cohosts ### Rules Standard Forum Rules. No being an arse, cheating, spamming etc. Days will last 4 IRL days. Nights will last 3 IRL days. Extensions will not be granted for forgetting to send an action without fair reason. (sorry about this im new to the terminology) Voting is **not** compulsive, but is plurality based, while majority w/ hammer and NoLynch are in effect. At the end of the day the option with the most votes will be processed, but if an option reaches majority (with the exception of NoLynch, which needs majority for 6 hrs straight) it will be processed instantly. if something reaches hammer (again, besides NoLynch) please cease posting. Roles ARE revealed upon death
### Gameplay Days will be 4 IRL days long, or shorter if someone dies Nights will be 3 IRL days long Actions are done by submitting them in your role chat Evil Faction will talk through a combined PM on the forums Upon joining, PM me, Night and htm a name one could use for a class/role. This PM is your role chat from here on out Once everyone has joined and sent a name, I will randomly assign a name to each person. **You may receive your own name** I will also assign factions at this time. Once you have these you must make a class/role card to go along with your name. I reserve the right to deny your class/role card choice for any reason. I also reserve the right to Rules Lawyer™ you on the syntax of your card :wink:, so be careful! The thread will be locked at this time to avoid pregame scum reading which may or may not have happened in some *other* [X]pick game. :stuck_out_tongue: Generally, try to keep the cards from being OP (nobody likes 1 person controlling the entire), however the more apt/creative/thematically fitting the card is with the name, the more powerful I'll accept. (Weird/original mechanics especially) This should go without saying, but beware bastard mechanics, as they may be present (see previous parentheses) ### Executions To accuse someone say "**/accuse [player]**" or "**/vote [player]**" on a separate line When someone has enough votes, they will be lynched Executions end the Day
### After The Night You will be told what happened to you >**Night:** Who knows! **Day:** Who knows!: The Sequel ### Journals Message me your entire journal, the last draft I receive before you die shall be the one displayed
### To Join To join, simply express interest in joining by saying something like "I want to join" or "/join" or "/in" or "sign me up, coach" or whatever you want, bolded
### Rolelist: Proposed rolelist: **Evil** **Evil** **Evil** [color=#23F71B]Town Town Town Town Town Town Town Town Town Town[/color] [color=lightgray]Neutral killer/non-killer[/color] [color=lightgray]Neutral non-killer[/color] #### Players: 1. **Boss** 2. **Insanity** 3. **Pkr** 1. **Samantha** 1. **POWmerist** 1. **Marl** 1. **Max** 1. **MtheBatman** 1. **Eevee** 1. **Wolfy** 1. **Pug** 1. **Nerbins** 1. **Popplio** 2. **Nuclear** 15. **Jammy**
---- # Oh yeah, I almost forgot to mention: bonuses to strength of card also apply to name originality, but dont go over the top with it ######
